# IntelliGrid — Complete Technical Audit
> Version 2.4.0 | Audited: May 2026

---

## 1. Platform Overview

IntelliGrid is a **production SaaS AI tools discovery platform** that aggregates, enriches, and monetizes access to AI tool listings. It operates as a marketplace with a freemium/subscription model, automated data pipelines, and programmatic SEO.

- **Live URL:** https://www.intelligrid.online
- **Backend:** Node.js ESM + Express → Railway
- **Frontend:** React 18 + Vite + Tailwind → Vercel
- **Database:** MongoDB Atlas
- **Cache:** Redis (Upstash)
- **Search:** Algolia
- **Auth:** Clerk
- **Payments:** PayPal (USD, global) + Cashfree (INR, India)
- **Error Tracking:** Sentry
- **Notifications:** Telegram Bot (owner alerts + community bot)
- **Email:** Resend (transactional)

