## 5. Enrichment Pipeline

### Architecture

```
Tool (needsEnrichment=true OR enrichmentScore < 50)
  ↓
[1] scrapeToolWebsite()     — Cheerio HTTP scraper
  ↓ title, metaDesc, h1, h2s, bodyText, ogImage, twitterHandle
[2] enrichWithGroq()        — LLaMA-3.1-8b-instant via Groq API
  ↓ 20-field JSON response
[3] buildUpdatePayload()    — Merge (never overwrite populated fields)
[4] resolveCategoryId()     — Auto-assign MongoDB Category ObjectId
[5] computeEnrichmentScore() — 0-100 quality score
[6] Tool.findByIdAndUpdate() — Save to MongoDB
[7] syncToolToAlgolia()     — Non-blocking Algolia re-index
```

### Groq Key Rotator

- Supports up to 10 Groq API keys (`GROQ_API_KEY` through `GROQ_API_KEY_10`)
- Lazy-initialized on first enrichment call (prevents startup crash if key missing)
- Handles **TPD (tokens per day)** limit: marks key exhausted, rotates to next
- Handles **TPM (tokens per minute)** limit: parses retry-after header, waits, retries same key (max 2 retries)
- If all keys exhausted: throws `DailyTokenLimitError` → stops the batch cleanly

### Groq Prompt Output (20 fields)

`pricingModel`, `startingPrice`, `hasFreeVersion`, `hasFreeTrialDays`, `hasAPI`, `platforms[]`, `useCaseTags[]`, `audienceTags[]`, `industryTags[]`, `integrationTags[]`, `keyFeatures[]`, `useCaseExamples[]`, `longDescription`, `seoTitle`, `seoDescription`, `seoKeywords[]`, `targetAudience`, `alternativeTo[]`, `companyName`, `foundedYear`, `hqCountry`, `twitterHandle`, `isActivelyMaintained`

### Enrichment Score Formula (0-100)

| Signal | Points |
|---|---|
| shortDescription > 80 chars | 8 |
| longDescription > 200 chars | 12 |
| screenshotUrl (< 30 days old) | 15 |
| screenshotUrl (> 30 days old) | 5 |
| pricing set (not Unknown) | 8 |
| hasFreeTier set | 4 |
| useCaseTags >= 3 | 10 |
| useCaseTags >= 7 (bonus) | 5 |
| audienceTags >= 1 | 5 |
| industryTags >= 1 | 3 |
| platforms >= 1 | 6 |
| keyFeatures >= 3 | 8 |
| alternativeTo >= 1 | 5 |
| videoEmbedUrl set | 7 |
| metaTitle + metaDescription | 4 |
| targetAudience set | 3 |
| humanVerified = true | 5 |

### Batch Selection

`getEnrichmentBatch(50)` selects tools where:
- `status` in `[active, pending, auto_approved]`
- `isActive != false`
- `lastEnrichedAt` is null OR `enrichmentScore < 50` OR last enriched > 30 days ago

Sorted by `enrichmentScore ASC, lastEnrichedAt ASC` (lowest quality first).

