## 6. Crawler / Discovery System

### Crawler Scheduler (`crawlerScheduler.js`)

Runs every **4 hours**. Tasks per run:
1. Run all registered source crawlers (Futurepedia, Taaft, AITools.fyi)
2. Deduplicate against existing tools by `officialUrl` / `externalId`
3. Insert new tools with `status: 'auto_approved'`, `isNew: true`, `needsEnrichment: true`
4. Run Groq enrichment batch on newly discovered + unenriched tools
5. Flag dead links via `linkHealthChecker`

### Category Normalizer (`normalizer.js`)

Maps free-text tags/categories from scrapers to IntelliGrid's canonical category slugs. Used by `resolveCategoryId()` to auto-assign categories during enrichment.

### Link Health Checker

Periodically HEAD-requests tool URLs. Updates `linkStatus` field to `active`, `dead`, or `redirected`. Dead tools are flagged for admin review.

