## 7. Cron Jobs

| Cron | Schedule | Tasks |
|---|---|---|
| `trialCron` | Daily 08:00 UTC | Expire trials → downgrade to Free; Day 12 urgency email; Day 11 reminder; Day 7 midpoint nudge |
| `winBackCron` | Daily | Sequences for churned users: D+1, D+3, D+7, D+14 emails |
| `enrichmentCron` | Daily 03:00 UTC | Recompute trendingScores; reset isNew (>30 days); flag stale tools (>70 days) |
| `trendingCron` | Daily 03:00 UTC | Backup: mark top 10 by trendingScore as isTrending |
| `crawlerScheduler` | Every 4 hours | Crawl sources; import new tools; Groq batch enrichment |

### Trending Score Formula

```
trendingScore =
  (weeklyViews × 2.0)
+ (weeklyBookmarks × 3.5)
+ (recentReviews[14d] × 4.0)
+ (enrichmentScore × 0.3)
+ (isFeatured ? 10 : 0)
+ (isNew ? 8 : 0)
- min(daysSinceEnriched × 0.1, 20)
```

Top 20 by trendingScore → `isTrending = true`. Weekly counters reset every Monday.

