## 9. Security & RBAC

### Role Hierarchy

```
USER < MODERATOR < ADMIN < SUPER_ADMIN
```

`getRoleLevel()` returns numeric rank for comparison. `requireRole('ADMIN')` middleware blocks lower roles.

### Rate Limiting (per-endpoint)

| Endpoint | Limit |
|---|---|
| Auth routes | 10 req/15 min |
| Tool submission | 5 req/hour |
| Search | 60 req/min |
| General API | 100 req/15 min |
| Webhook routes | No rate limit (IP whitelisted) |

### Other Security

- `mongo-sanitize` on all request bodies
- Sort field whitelist in `toolController.js` (prevents field enumeration via Mongoose sort)
- Helmet sets: CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type-Options
- CORS: only `FRONTEND_URL` + localhost origins allowed

