## 14. Known Issues & Current State

### Resolved (Recent Fixes)

- **BUG-04:** Subscription activation used timing heuristic → fixed with `getPlanIdMap()` reverse lookup
- **BUG-07:** Sort field enumeration attack vector → fixed with `ALLOWED_SORT_FIELDS` whitelist
- **BUG-11:** PLAN_MAP copy-pasted 3x → extracted to module-level constant
- **BUG-13:** Cashfree webhook deduplication used wrong field → fixed to use `cf_payment_id`
- **BUG-14:** Webhook body was re-serialized (breaking HMAC) → fixed with `express.raw()` + Buffer parsing
- **isEnriched bug:** Was only set inside `if(categoryId)` block → caused infinite re-enrichment loop → fixed to always set
- **Groq initialization:** Was eagerly initialized (crashed if no key) → fixed to lazy-init

### In Progress

- Affiliate-to-tool matching pipeline (passive revenue)
- Newsletter CTA expansion across all landing pages
- Vendor claim workflow finalization (B2B outreach)
- Admin enrichment stats/reporting improvements

