- `CRAWLER_ENABLED=true` must be set in Railway for discovery to run
- All 6 PayPal Billing Plan IDs must be set for subscription renewal webhooks to map correctly
- Cashfree must be in `production` mode with real APP_ID/SECRET
- PayPal webhook URL must be registered in PayPal Developer dashboard: `POST /api/v1/payment/webhooks/paypal`
